BEAUTIFUL ?

12:08.630 --> 12:10.791
YEAH, IT IS.

12:10.800 --> 12:12.256
HE'S GOOD.

12:12.260 --> 12:15.297
YEAH, HE IS
REALLY GOOD.

12:15.300 --> 12:18.690
I ONLY WISH
HE BELIEVED THAT.

12:28.200 --> 12:30.555
THIS ONE'S GOT
REAL ATTITUDE.

12:30.560 --> 12:32.790
OH, MY GOD.

12:32.800 --> 12:34.427
THE LIGHT'S
SPECTACULAR.

12:34.430 --> 12:37.524
BRENDA, THAT IS A PICTURE
OF ME URINATING ON A WALL.

12:37.530 --> 12:39.828
I REALIZE THAT.

12:39.830 --> 12:40.990
HEY, WHAT DO
YOU THINK ?

12:41.000 --> 12:42.592
WHAT, SO, NOW
YOU'RE STALKING ME ?

12:42.600 --> 12:44.454
NO, NO, I JUST HAPPENED
TO SEE YOU ONE DAY

12:44.460 --> 12:45.757
WHEN I WAS OUT
TAKING PICTURES.

12:45.760 --> 12:47.125
SO, I FOLLOWED YOU
FOR A COUPLE OF MILES.

12:47.130 --> 12:48.620
OH, YEAH, YOU WERE JUST
OUT TAKING PICTURES ?

12:48.630 --> 12:50.222
YOU LIVE IN
FUCKING VENICE.

12:50.230 --> 12:51.697
THERE'S NO REASON FOR YOU
TO BE IN MY NEIGHBORHOOD.

12:51.700 --> 12:52.997
WOW.

12:53.000 --> 12:54.627
YOU REALLY THINK THE WORLD
REVOLVES AROUND YOU, DON'T YOU ?

12:54.630 --> 12:57.098
BREN, WOULD YOU TELL HIM, PLEASE
THIS ISN'T ABOUT HIM ?

13:00.660 --> 13:03.891
IT'S WHAT
BILLY DOES.

13:03.900 --> 13:06.551
HE TAKES PICTURES OF PEOPLE
WHEN THEY'RE OFF GUARD.

13:06.560 --> 13:08.596
HE'S GOT A TALENT,
IT'S ART.

13:08.600 --> 13:10.329
NO, IT'S FUCKED !

13:15.860 --> 13:17.691
THANKS A LOT.

13:27.360 --> 13:28.554
LOOK !

13:28.560 --> 13:31.529
THAT'S YOUR SON
PISSING AGAINST A WALL !

13:33.930 --> 13:36.296
SO, I SHOULD JUST LET HIM
HUMILIATE ME WHENEVER HE WANTS ?

13:36.300 --> 13:38.621
OH, GOD, NATE,
DON'T MAKE THIS ABOUT YOU.

13:38.630 --> 13:40.325
WELL, WHY THE
FUCK NOT ?

13:40.330 --> 13:41.752
THIS IS ABOUT ME.

13:41.760 --> 13:43.398
YOU CERTAINLY MAKE ENOUGH
STUFF ALL ABOUT YOU.

13:45.860 --> 13:48.021
WHO GOT HURT,
WHO DIED ?

13:50.260 --> 13:52.490
YOU DON'T THINK I HAVE A RIGHT
TO NOT BE SPIED UPON ?

13:52.500 --> 13:56.049
YOU'RE TALKING TO SOMEBODY WHO
WAS SPIED ON HER WHOLE LIFE.

13:56.060 --> 13:59.518
GOD, BILLY IS SEVERELY
FUCKED UP, BREN.

13:59.530 --> 14:01.157
I DON'T LIKE BEING
STALKED BY A PSYCHO.

14:01.160 --> 14:02.752
BILLY IS
NOT PSYCHOTIC !

14:02.760 --> 14:04.398
HE HAS A DISEASE !

14:04.400 --> 14:06.356
HE'S FINE WHEN HE
TAKES HIS MEDS.

14:06.360 --> 14:08.123
YEAH, WELL,
WHEN THE FUCK IS THAT ?

14:13.360 --> 14:16.056
LOOK, HAS HE EVER
DONE ANYTHING WEIRD ?

14:16.060 --> 14:18.722
UH, YEAH,
HE'S BIPOLAR.

14:18.730 --> 14:21.198
HIS WHOLE LIFE
HE'S BEEN WEIRD.

14:21.200 --> 14:25.398
HAS HE EVER DONE
ANYTHING DANGEROUS ?

14:26.230 --> 14:28.721
OH, GOD...

14:28.730 --> 14:30.891
NATE, NO.

14:32.360 --> 14:36.091
THE ONLY PERSON BILLY WOULD
EVER BE A THREAT TO...

14:36.100 --> 14:37.852
IS HIMSELF.

14:37.860 --> 14:39.657
HAS HE EVER
TRIED TO--

14:39.660 --> 14:41.298
YES.

14:42.830 --> 14:44.195
WHEN I WAS 18.

14:48.600 --> 14:50.659
I WENT TO EUROPE
FOR THREE MONTHS.

14:50.660 --> 14:53.754
IT WAS THIS BIG REWARD FOR ME
WINNING A SCHOLARSHIP TO YALE.

14:55.730 --> 14:58.290
WHEN I GOT BACK TO L.A.,
MY MOTHER WAS AT THE AIRPORT.

14:58.300 --> 15:02.020
SHE TOLD ME THAT BILLY
HAD COMMITTED SUICIDE.

15:03.230 --> 15:08.156
MY WHOLE LIFE JUST COLLAPSED
IN ON ITSELF IN THAT MOMENT.

15:10.230 --> 15:12.949
OF COURSE, SHE MEANT TO
SAY THAT BILLY HAD...

15:12.960 --> 15:15.224
TRIED TO
COMMIT SUICIDE.

15:15.230 --> 15:17.221
SHE WAS DRUNK,
OR ELSE...

15:17.230 --> 15:20.654
IT WAS
A FREUDIAN SLIP.

15:23.330 --> 15:24.957
YOU NEVER WENT
TO YALE.

15:24.960 --> 15:27.428
BILLY WAS IN A HOSPITAL
IN PASADENA.

15:27.430 --> 15:31.753
I TOOK SOME CLASSES
AT U.C.L.A. IN THE SPRING.

15:31.760 --> 15:35.196
THEN IN THE FALL,

15:35.200 --> 15:37.589
HE WAS DIAGNOSED
MANIC DEPRESSIVE,

15:37.600 --> 15:39.022
WHICH KICKS IN
IN ADOLESCENCE,

15:39.030 --> 15:40.429
SO, IT PROBABLY HAD
NOTHING TO DO WITH ME

15:40.430 --> 15:41.954
GETTING THE SCHOLARSHIP.

15:41.960 --> 15:44.793
I CAN'T BELIEVE THEY PRESSURED
YOU INTO SACRIFICING YOUR LIFE

15:44.800 --> 15:46.222
FOR YOUR BROTHER.

15:46.230 --> 15:47.652
NOBODY PRESSURED ME.

15:49.260 --> 15:51.728
I WANTED TO STAY.

15:58.500 --> 16:00.525
( Nate )
MORNING.

16:00.530 --> 16:02.851
PEE ON ANY
WALLS LATELY ?

16:02.860 --> 16:04.396
SHUT UP.

16:06.700 --> 16:09.089
SO, MOM, WHAT'S WITH
YOU AND NIKOLAI ?

16:09.100 --> 16:11.489
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

16:13.160 --> 16:14.422
AND DAVE...

16:14.430 --> 16:16.751
WHAT'D YOU DO
LAST NIGHT ?

16:16.760 --> 16:17.954
NOTHING.

16:17.960 --> 16:19.757
SATURDAY NIGHT,
WHAT HAPPENED TO THAT--

16:20.860 --> 16:23.624
PERSON YOU'RE
SEEING ?

16:25.130 --> 16:27.997
UH, THAT PERSON IS
NO LONGER IN THE PICTURE.

16:28.000 --> 16:29.297
SORRY TO HEAR IT.

16:29.300 --> 16:32.098
WHAT ABOUT YOU ?

16:33.660 --> 16:35.025
ARE YOU DATING
ANYBODY ?

16:35.030 --> 16:36.156
NO.

16:36.160 --> 16:37.627
IF YOU'RE
DATING SOMEONE,

16:37.630 --> 16:39.393
YOU DON'T NEED TO HIDE HIM
FROM US LIKE WE'RE LEPERS.

16:39.400 --> 16:40.958
I'M NOT
DATING ANYONE.

16:40.960 --> 16:44.054
I'VE JUST BEEN HANGING OUT
A LOT WITH SOMEBODY.

16:44.060 --> 16:45.948
WHO IS
THIS PERSON ?

16:48.960 --> 16:50.757
NOBODY.

16:52.860 --> 16:55.397
DAVID, I'M READY
TO GO TO CHURCH.

17:00.600 --> 17:02.295
THAN KS, GUYS.

17:04.730 --> 17:06.698
Hey, Joey,
the kid's ready.

17:06.700 --> 17:08.099
So am I.

17:12.930 --> 17:16.457
This is the most terrifying
shower scene since "Psycho".

17:17.660 --> 17:19.696
(video game sounds )

17:20.630 --> 17:23.656
THAT FOOTBALL GAME USED TO MAKE
THIS REALLY OBNOXIOUS NOISE

17:23.660 --> 17:25.298
WHEN YOU SCORED
A TOUCHDOWN.

17:27.100 --> 17:29.751
DO YOU WANT TO SHOW ME
HOW TO PLAY IT ?

17:29.760 --> 17:32.149
NO.

17:35.200 --> 17:36.792
YOU KNOW,
THERE'S THIS...

17:36.800 --> 17:40.952
THERE'S THIS LITTLE KID
NEXT DOOR AND...

17:40.960 --> 17:43.349
I MEAN, THE ONLY TOY HE'S GOT IS
LIKE THIS STUPID MOUSETRAP GAME

17:43.360 --> 17:45.294
FROM WHEN HIS
MOM WAS A KID.

17:46.560 --> 17:48.027
MAYBE...

17:48.030 --> 17:50.021
YOU KNOW, HE'D WANT
SOME OF THESE.

18:00.960 --> 18:02.552
IT'S A BEAUTIFUL DAY.

18:02.560 --> 18:05.154
WHY WOULD YOU WASTE YOUR SUNDAY
IN HERE WATCHING TELEVISION ?

18:10.600 --> 18:11.919
WHAT ARE
YOU DOING ?

18:13.530 --> 18:15.555
UMM...

18:15.560 --> 18:18.097
I THOUGHT THAT
TONY RECHNER NEXT DOOR
MIGHT WANT SOME OF THESE.

18:22.230 --> 18:24.027
JUST KEEP YOUR
HANDS OFF THEM.

18:30.860 --> 18:33.226
SHE DOESN'T EVEN LOOK ME
IN THE EYES ANYMORE.

18:43.100 --> 18:45.056
C'MON, I WANT TO SHOW YOU
SOMETHING FUNNY.

18:45.060 --> 18:46.493
COME ON.

18:49.500 --> 18:50.819
COME ON.

18:54.360 --> 18:56.123
WE'RE GOING ON
A FIELD TRIP ?

18:58.200 --> 19:00.020
THIS IS LIKE
THE FIRST DAY OF SCHOOL.

19:00.030 --> 19:02.692
I AM SO EXCITED.

19:02.700 --> 19:04.691
OH, AND...

19:04.700 --> 19:06.918
I JUST WANT TO APOLOGIZE
IN ADVANCE

19:06.930 --> 19:09.091
BECAUSE I HAD CALAMARI
LAST NIGHT FOR DINNER.

19:09.100 --> 19:10.658
WHAT DO
YOU MEAN ?

19:10.660 --> 19:12.355
WELL, LET'S JUST SAY
THIS IS THE ONE TIME

19:12.360 --> 19:13.827
WHERE THE STRONG
SMELL OF FORMALDEHYDE

19:13.830 --> 19:16.355
REALLY COMES
IN HAN DY.

19:19.960 --> 19:21.291
SO, THEN I SAID
TO HIM

19:21.300 --> 19:23.256
"I DON'T CARE IF YOU HAVE
A LOW SPERM COUNT.

19:23.260 --> 19:25.399
"I MEAN, I'LL JUST SHOVE
A TURKEY BASTER UP THERE

19:25.400 --> 19:26.890
IF I HAVE TO."

19:26.900 --> 19:29.289
I WANT TO HAVE A CHILD
BEFORE I TURN 40.

19:29.300 --> 19:30.858
THAT'S FAIR, RIGHT ?

19:30.860 --> 19:32.327
HELLO, EVERYONE.

19:32.330 --> 19:33.695
HI.

19:33.700 --> 19:35.622
HOW WAS CHURCH ?

19:35.630 --> 19:37.495
NATE TOLD ME
YOU'RE A DEACON.

19:37.500 --> 19:39.491
THAT'S ADORABLE.

19:46.100 --> 19:47.954
I SEE YOU'VE MADE
YOURSELF AT HOME.

19:47.960 --> 19:51.657
ANGELA DOESN'T LIKE
TO FEEL CONSTRAINED.

19:51.660 --> 19:54.254
YOU KNOW, MY GLANDS
GO DOUBLE-TIME.

19:54.260 --> 19:56.296
I FIND IF I WEAR
TOO MUCH WHILE I WORK,

19:56.300 --> 19:57.449
I GET ALL...

19:57.460 --> 19:58.597
PITTED.

20:07.000 --> 20:08.399
ANGELA...

20:08.400 --> 20:10.493
WE'RE SORT OF USED TO A MORE
PROFESSIONAL APPEARANCE

20:10.500 --> 20:12.024
AROUND HERE.

20:12.030 --> 20:13.327
GIVE ME
A BREAK, DAVID.

20:13.330 --> 20:14.649
THEY'RE JUST
NIPPLES.

20:14.660 --> 20:17.356
I MEAN, WE'VE ALL SEEN 'EM,
WE'VE ALL TOUCHED 'EM.

20:17.360 --> 20:18.896
WE'VE ALL
SUCKED ON 'EM.

20:18.900 --> 20:20.959
AND IT'S NOT LIKE THIS GUY
IS GONNA BE LYING IN THE CASKET

20:20.960 --> 20:22.359
AND PEOPLE ARE
GONNA BE SAYING,

20:22.360 --> 20:24.828
"OH, MY GOD, THE EMBALMER'S
NIPPLES WERE HARD."

20:24.830 --> 20:26.422
THERE GONNA BE SAYING,

20:26.430 --> 20:28.250
"OH, MY GOD, HOW DID THEY
PUT HIS FACE BACK TOGETHER

20:28.260 --> 20:30.899
AFTER HE WENT THROUGH
THE GODDAMN WINDSHIELD ?"

20:32.930 --> 20:34.989
I TOLD FATHER JACK
I'D HELP HIM WITH

20:35.000 --> 20:36.922
THE FOOD DISTRIBUTION
DOWNTOWN.

20:36.930 --> 20:39.421
I JUST WANTED TO MAKE SURE THAT
YOUR FIRST DAY WAS GOING OKAY.

20:39.430 --> 20:40.692
THAN KS.

20:40.700 --> 20:43.225
I'M ALL GASSY,
BUT THAT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

20:43.230 --> 20:45.858
ANGELA HAD CALAMARI
LAST NIGHT.

20:49.030 --> 20:50.850
BOY, HE'S A BARREL
OF LAUGHS.

20:50.860 --> 20:52.851
( laughing )

20:53.700 --> 20:56.089
IT'S HARD WHEN A NEW PERSON
COMES INTO A SITUATION.

20:56.100 --> 20:57.954
IT THROWS
EVERYTHING OFF BALANCE.

20:57.960 --> 21:01.953
BREN, I'M NOT THREATENED
BY YOUR BOYFRIEND.

21:01.960 --> 21:03.791
OH, YEAH ?

21:03.800 --> 21:07.054
YOUR BEHAVIOR CONSISTENTLY
COMMUNICATES OTHERWISE.

21:08.560 --> 21:11.996
OKAY, YOU WANT ME
TO TAKE THE PICTURE
OUT OF THE SHOW, FINE.

21:12.000 --> 21:13.797
BUT PLEASE DON'T SPOUT
PSYCHO-BABBLE AT ME

21:13.800 --> 21:15.427
LIKE FUCKING
MARGARET AND BERNARD.

21:15.430 --> 21:16.852
YOU'RE LIKE,
BECOMING THEM.

21:16.860 --> 21:17.997
FUCK YOU !

21:18.000 --> 21:19.649
YOU KNOW WHAT
YOU DID WAS WRONG.

21:19.660 --> 21:21.355
THAT'S WHY YOU DIDN'T
SHOW IT TO ME BEFORE.

21:21.360 --> 21:23.089
WHY ARE YOU MAKING SUCH
A BIG DEAL OUT OF THIS ?

21:23.100 --> 21:24.897
BECAUSE
I LOVE HIM !

21:29.930 --> 21:33.320
YOU'RE FUCKING WITH MY LIFE,
BILLY, AND IT'S NOT FAIR.

21:33.330 --> 21:35.218
YOU HAVE TO STOP.

21:36.430 --> 21:38.125
OR WHAT ?

21:38.130 --> 21:38.949
GODDAMNIT, BILLY !

21:38.960 --> 21:40.496
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU,

21:40.500 --> 21:42.798
YOU LIKE FUCKING WITH
MY BRAIN LIKE FEINBERG ?!

21:54.960 --> 21:56.427
THANK YOU.

21:56.430 --> 21:57.795
YOU'RE WELCOME.

22:00.560 --> 22:02.528
CAN I GET YOU
ANYTHING ELSE ?

22:02.530 --> 22:05.624
I CAN ALWAYS USE
A GOOD BLOW JOB...

22:09.600 --> 22:12.922
HEY, DO I GET
MY FUCKING LUNCH OR NOT ?

22:16.800 --> 22:19.052
I'M GOING TO GET
A DRINK OF WATER.

22:21.830 --> 22:23.354
MELINDA DANER,

22:23.360 --> 22:25.294
MARK WHITMAN...

22:25.300 --> 22:27.723
DARRYL HEINZ,

22:27.730 --> 22:29.698
KEITH CHARLES.

22:29.700 --> 22:31.895
OKAY, WELL, JUST TELL
THEM WE'LL MEET THEM

22:31.900 --> 22:33.754
AT THE USUAL CORNER
ON TUESDAY.

22:33.760 --> 22:35.296
HI, TRACY.

22:35.300 --> 22:37.097
OH, HI, DAVID.

22:37.100 --> 22:39.227
HOW HAVE YOU BEEN ?

22:39.230 --> 22:40.822
FINE.

22:40.830 --> 22:42.525
I LOVE YOUR
NEW HAIR.

22:42.530 --> 22:44.748
WHAT ARE YOU
WORKING ON ?

22:44.760 --> 22:48.753
ST. STEPHEN'S IS SENDING
OVER SOME VOLUNTEERS

22:48.760 --> 22:50.625
TO HELP OUT NEXT WEEK.

22:50.630 --> 22:53.599
SOMEONE TOLD ME THAT YOU
USED TO GO TO ST. STEPHEN'S.

22:53.600 --> 22:55.818
NOT THAT I'VE BEEN ASKING
AROUND ABOUT YOU.

22:55.830 --> 22:57.593
IT JUST CAME
UP NATURALLY.

22:57.600 --> 22:58.851
SO, DID YOU ?

22:58.860 --> 23:00.327
GO THERE, I MEAN.

23:00.330 --> 23:01.922
YEAH, JUST FOR
A FEW MONTHS LAST YEAR.

23:01.930 --> 23:04.524
THEY'RE A VERY
PROGRESSIVE CHURCH.

23:04.530 --> 23:06.293
YES, THEY ARE.

23:11.560 --> 23:14.723
THE GUY WHO TOOK THESE
IS A TOTAL PSYCHO.

23:20.900 --> 23:22.094
GOOD.

23:24.000 --> 23:25.752
WE SHOULD PROBABLY GET GOING
IF WE WANT TO SEE THAT MOVIE.

23:25.760 --> 23:29.321
I SHOULD PROBABLY
GET HOME.

23:29.330 --> 23:31.491
AND CHECK ON MY MOM.

23:31.500 --> 23:33.923
I'M SURE
SHE'S DOING FINE.

23:38.100 --> 23:39.522
I'M SORRY.

23:39.530 --> 23:41.691
IT'S NOT LIKE I WAS
DYING TO SEE A MOVIE.

23:41.700 --> 23:43.952
THAT'S NOT WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

23:47.530 --> 23:49.498
I'M SORRY...

23:49.500 --> 23:52.492
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
BETWEEN US.

23:52.500 --> 23:56.550
I NEVER MEANT FOR THOSE ASSHOLES
TO WRITE SHIT ON YOUR CAR.

23:58.000 --> 23:59.797
I SHOULDN'T HAVE
TOLD ANDY ABOUT US.

23:59.800 --> 24:02.257
I WAS JUST
BEING STUPID.

24:02.260 --> 24:06.026
THAT WAS ME BEING
REALLY, REALLY,
REALLY STUPID AND...

24:09.600 --> 24:11.659
I'M SORRY.

24:15.600 --> 24:17.898
WELL, THANK YOU.

24:34.860 --> 24:37.556
LOOK, I DON'T WANT TO MAKE
A BIG DEAL OUT OF THIS.

24:37.560 --> 24:40.449
ALL I'M SAYING IS
I SAT AROUND LAST WEEK

24:40.460 --> 24:42.951
IN THAT STUPID GET-UP
YOU WANTED ME TO WEAR

24:42.960 --> 24:44.825
AND HAD TO SAY
ALL THIS

24:44.830 --> 24:46.889
DADDY THIS AND
DADDY THAT BULLSHIT.

24:46.900 --> 24:49.994
WHEN I TELL YOU, I KEEP
READING THESE ARTICLES

24:50.000 --> 24:51.752
ABOUT HAVING THIS
ONE-HOUR ORGASM,

24:51.760 --> 24:54.593
WELL, THE LEAST YOU COULD DO
IS TRY TO HELP ME HAVE ONE.

24:54.600 --> 24:57.228
WELL, I'M SORRY THAT
MEN CAN'T HAVE IT.

24:57.230 --> 24:59.425
BUT SINCE YOU GUYS GET TO HAVE
EVERYTHING ELSE ON THE PLANET,

24:59.430 --> 25:01.398
IT SEEMS LIKE
A FAIR TRADE-OFF.

25:02.530 --> 25:03.554
FINE.

25:03.560 --> 25:05.096
GOODBYE.

25:07.730 --> 25:09.254
YOU KNOW...

25:09.260 --> 25:11.057
ANGELA, MY BROTHER
LIKES A CERTAIN DECORUM

25:11.060 --> 25:14.598
WHEN YOU'RE WORKING
WITH SOMEONE'S LOVED ONE.

25:14.600 --> 25:16.227
YEAH ?

25:16.230 --> 25:19.597
THE PERSONAL CALLS ARE
A PROBABLY LITTLE UNCOOL.

25:19.600 --> 25:22.023
OH, RIGHT, GOT IT.

25:22.030 --> 25:23.657
I WON'T DO IT
WHEN HE'S AROUND.

25:24.130 --> 25:25.722
( phone )

25:27.400 --> 25:28.628
HELLO ?

25:30.360 --> 25:31.554
HEY.

25:33.560 --> 25:34.754
REALLY ?

25:34.760 --> 25:36.398
WHY DON'T YOU
WANT ME TO COME OVER ?

25:36.400 --> 25:39.119
DAMNIT, BRENDA,
YOU ALWAYS DO THIS.

25:39.130 --> 25:40.449
YOU'RE SHUTTING
ME OUT.

25:40.460 --> 25:43.099
THE PISSING THING IS
NO LONGER AN ISSUE, I SWEAR.

25:43.100 --> 25:45.898
LOOK, MAYBE YOU'D FEEL
BETTER IF I CAME OVER.

25:45.900 --> 25:49.222
ALRIGHT, FINE,
WHATEVER, FINE.

25:52.760 --> 25:53.920
WHOO !

25:53.930 --> 25:55.750
GIRLFRIEND TROUBLE ?

25:55.760 --> 25:57.057
NOT REALLY TROUBLE.

25:57.060 --> 25:58.288
JUST TELL ME WHAT
THE FIGHT WAS ABOUT

25:58.300 --> 26:00.621
AND I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT TO SAY TO FIX IT.

26:00.630 --> 26:02.257
I MEAN, TRUST ME
THIS IS MY THING.

26:02.260 --> 26:03.454
WE DIDN'T
HAVE A FIGHT.

26:03.460 --> 26:04.893
SHE JUST...

26:04.900 --> 26:08.358
PULLS AWAY FROM ME
AT THE WEIRDEST TIMES.

26:10.100 --> 26:11.419
MAYBE SHE
SENSES THAT...

26:11.430 --> 26:13.751
YOU'RE PULLING AWAY,

26:13.760 --> 26:15.421
SO, SHE JUST
DOES IT FIRST.

26:15.430 --> 26:18.297
MAYBE YOU SHOULD MIND
YOUR OWN BUSINESS.

26:18.300 --> 26:19.494
SHOOT.

26:19.500 --> 26:21.752
I GUESS THIS MEANS I CAN'T
ASK ABOUT THE PISSING ?

26:21.760 --> 26:24.593
'CAUSE I HAD AN EX
WHO WANTED TO PEE ON ME.

26:24.600 --> 26:26.397
AND I WASN'T
GROSSED OUT.

26:26.400 --> 26:28.391
I MEAN, I JUST THOUGHT
IT WAS KIND OF SILLY,

26:28.400 --> 26:29.856
BUT THAT'S ME.

26:50.800 --> 26:54.554
THANK YOU FOR TAKING ME
TO THE ART GALLERY LAST NIGHT.

26:54.560 --> 26:57.199
I THOUGHT YOU HATED
THOSE PICTURES.

26:57.200 --> 26:58.292
NO, NO...

26:58.300 --> 27:01.098
IT'S JUST THAT I DON'T
LIKE THEM, THAT'S ALL.

27:01.100 --> 27:03.751
BUT IT WAS NICE TO BE
SPENDING TIME WITH YOU.

27:03.760 --> 27:07.696
I MEAN, OUTSIDE OF
WORKING TOGETHER.

27:09.660 --> 27:11.821
WOULD YOU LIKE TO GO
TO DINNER SOME TIME ?

27:11.830 --> 27:13.297
IS THAT
LIKE A...

27:13.300 --> 27:14.619
DATE ?

27:14.630 --> 27:16.450
OF COURSE NOT.

27:16.460 --> 27:19.099
GOOD, I PICK YOU UP
TOMORROW NIGHT, 8:00.

27:25.430 --> 27:26.692
I DON'T WANT
TO GO, OKAY ?

27:26.700 --> 27:28.099
JUST STOP ASKING ME.

27:28.100 --> 27:29.226
OKAY, FINE.

27:29.230 --> 27:30.891
I WAS ONLY INVITING YOU
TO BE NICE.

27:30.900 --> 27:32.322
BESIDES NOBODY EVEN
WANTS YOU THERE

27:32.330 --> 27:34.389
BECAUSE YOU'VE BEEN ACTING
SO FUCKING WEIRD LATELY.

27:34.400 --> 27:35.424
GABE ?

27:36.700 --> 27:39.191
WE HAVE TO BE
SOMEPLACE.

27:39.200 --> 27:40.258
GET LOST,
MORTICIA.

27:40.260 --> 27:42.057
SHUT UP,
PEANUT TESTICLE.

27:44.500 --> 27:45.558
FUCK OFF,

27:45.560 --> 27:46.891
BOTH OF YOU.

27:48.700 --> 27:50.224
WHAT'S HIS PROBLEM ?

27:50.230 --> 27:51.322
NOTHIN'...

27:51.330 --> 27:53.491
HE WANTS ME TO GO TO
THIS PARTY TOMORROW.

27:53.500 --> 27:54.922
I'M JUST NOT
IN THE MOOD.

27:54.930 --> 27:57.592
WE CAN DO SOMETHING
IF YOU WANT.

27:57.600 --> 27:59.488
ACTUALLY I GOTTA
GO TO BARSTOW TOMORROW

27:59.500 --> 28:01.058
AND SPEND THE NIGHT
AT MY DAD'S.

28:01.060 --> 28:04.052
I GOTTA ASK HIM
FOR MONEY FOR MY MOM.

28:04.060 --> 28:06.893
NOT THAT HE'S GONNA
GIVE IT TO ME, BUT.

28:08.560 --> 28:10.926
DO YOU WANT
COMPANY ?

28:10.930 --> 28:13.558
LOOK, CLAIRE, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO KEEP TAKING CARE OF ME.

28:13.560 --> 28:14.652
I'M NOT.

28:14.660 --> 28:17.493
I JUST LIKE
HANGING OUT.

28:19.360 --> 28:21.055
OR WE COULD JUST
GO FOR THE DRIVE

28:21.060 --> 28:23.096
AND THEN YOU GO SEE YOUR DAD
AND I'LL STAY IN SOME LIKE,

28:23.100 --> 28:25.591
CREEPY MOTEL AND READ
A STEPHEN KING BOOK.

28:27.130 --> 28:28.199
OKAY.

28:29.000 --> 28:32.151
MEET ME AFTER FIFTH PERIOD
TOMORROW BY THE GYM.

29:16.060 --> 29:18.255
OH, THIS IS JUST
WHAT I NEED TODAY.

29:18.260 --> 29:21.195
I SEE THIS IS PAYBACK TIME
FOR MY MISSING YOUR OPENING.

29:21.200 --> 29:22.622
JUST SHUT UP !

29:22.630 --> 29:24.894
BOTH OF YOU,
FOR ONCE.

29:24.900 --> 29:26.959
JUST SHUT YOUR
FUCKING MOUTHS.

29:26.960 --> 29:29.622
ALL THAT EVER COMES OUT OF YOU
IS GARBAGE, GARBAGE, GARBAGE !

29:29.630 --> 29:30.790
OKAY...

29:30.800 --> 29:32.392
GOOD,

29:32.400 --> 29:34.652
WE HAVE
A DIALOGUE.

29:38.260 --> 29:39.488
WHERE DID
YOU GET THIS ?

29:39.500 --> 29:40.956
FROM HIS OFFICE.

29:40.960 --> 29:42.655
THEY'RE EVERY PIECE OF DATA
FEINBERG HAS ON BRENDA

29:42.660 --> 29:44.196
AND IT'S ALL DESTROYED.

29:44.200 --> 29:46.828
NOW HE CAN GO BACK TO
WHEREVER HE CAME FROM
BEFORE HE FUCKED HER UP.

29:46.830 --> 29:48.957
YOU'RE OFF
THE HOOK, BERN.

29:48.960 --> 29:51.155
OBVIOUSLY THIS HAS NOTHING TO
DO WITH YOU MISSING HIS SHOW.

29:51.160 --> 29:53.594
DON'T FUCKING TALK ABOUT ME
LIKE I'M NOT HERE !

29:53.600 --> 29:56.990
EVEN THOUGH I'M NOT
AND NEVER HAVE BEEN.

29:57.000 --> 29:59.252
SON, WHAT'S WRONG ?
JUST TELL US.

29:59.260 --> 30:00.625
OH, THERE'S NOTHING
WRONG WITH ME.

30:00.630 --> 30:02.359
I DIDN'T SELL
MY DAUGHTER

30:02.360 --> 30:04.294
TO SOME SMUG,
STAR-FUCKING PSYCHIATRIST

30:04.300 --> 30:06.325
SO, HE COULD PICK HER APART
LIKE A GODDAMN CADAVER

30:06.330 --> 30:08.594
AND TURN HER INTO
SHIT AND GARBAGE

30:08.600 --> 30:10.352
JUST LIKE EVERYTHING
ELSE YOU TOUCH !

30:10.360 --> 30:11.327
BILLY,
SWEETH EART.

30:11.330 --> 30:12.456
YOU BITCH !

30:12.460 --> 30:13.950
YOU'RE THE FUCKING NURSE.

30:13.960 --> 30:16.758
YOU WANNA TIE US UP,
YOU WANNA LOCK US IN A ROOM,
LEAVE US TO DIE.

30:16.760 --> 30:18.990
WELL, YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT SHOULD DIE, YOU AND HIM !

30:19.000 --> 30:21.457
YOU DON'T GET TO
TOUCH THE CHILDREN.

30:22.760 --> 30:24.899
I REFUSE TO BE
AN AUDIENCE FOR THIS.

30:34.800 --> 30:36.427
OH, BOY, YOU CAN
JUICE HER,

30:36.430 --> 30:38.751
BUT YOU BETTER LET ME
TAKE CARE OF THAT SKIN.

30:38.760 --> 30:42.548
THIS GUY HAS
A REALLY SINEWY NECK.

30:43.260 --> 30:44.522
SINEWY.

30:44.530 --> 30:46.350
I LOVE SAYING THAT WORD,
DON'T YOU ?

30:46.360 --> 30:47.918
I DON'T KNOW.

30:47.930 --> 30:50.228
I WENT OUT WITH THIS GUY ONCE,
HE HAD A REALLY SINEWY NECK.

30:50.230 --> 30:52.323
HE WAS A TOTAL
ANIMAL IN BED.

30:52.330 --> 30:54.298
I MEAN, THE THINGS HE COULD
DO WITH HIS TONGUE.

30:54.300 --> 30:55.790
( slurping )

30:55.800 --> 30:57.449
COURSE, HE THOUGHT HE WAS
GOD'S GIFT TO WOMEN.

30:57.460 --> 30:59.428
I GUESS IN THAT
ONE RESPECT HE WAS.

30:59.430 --> 31:02.126
SO, DO YOU LIKE
SINEWY NECKS, DAVID ?

31:02.130 --> 31:03.688
