PEOPLE I CAN SET YOU UP WITH.

31:10.460 --> 31:13.691
SO, WHAT KIND OF GUYS
DO YOU LIKE ?

31:13.700 --> 31:16.157
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THAT I LIKE MEN ?

31:16.160 --> 31:18.754
OH, PLEASE, LET'S NOT
PLAY THAT GAME.

31:19.860 --> 31:21.896
I THINK WE SHOULD
FIRE HER.

31:21.900 --> 31:23.197
I'VE BEEN THINKING
THE SAME THING.

31:23.200 --> 31:24.428
HAS SHE MADE A LOT
OF MISTAKES ?

31:24.430 --> 31:25.727
NO.

31:25.730 --> 31:27.891
SHE'S A LITTLE
HARD TO TAKE.

31:27.900 --> 31:29.299
SHE'S A LOT
HARD TO TAKE.

31:29.300 --> 31:31.450
SOMETIMES PEOPLE
ARE HARD TO TAKE,

31:31.460 --> 31:35.419
BUT ONLY BECAUSE THE FIRST SIDE
