31:35.430 --> 31:37.819
OR AGGRESSIVE
BECAUSE THEY'RE NERVOUS.

31:39.260 --> 31:40.955
AND IT'S ONLY AFTER
YOU SPEND SOME TIME WITH THEM

31:40.960 --> 31:42.621
YOU REALIZE MAYBE
THERE'S ANOTHER SIDE TO THEM

31:42.630 --> 31:44.097
THAT'S WORTH KNOWING.

31:47.430 --> 31:50.149
OR NOT, I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

31:50.960 --> 31:52.655
( door closing )

31:53.400 --> 31:55.391
SORRY I'M LATE.

31:55.400 --> 31:56.799
BY THE WAY...

31:56.800 --> 31:58.995
