FOR DINNER TOMORROW.

31:59.000 --> 32:00.228
SO, EVERYONE'S
ON THEIR OWN.

32:00.230 --> 32:01.629
ACTUALLY, I'M GOING
TO BE VOLUNTEERING

32:01.630 --> 32:02.790
WITH THE FOOD
DISTRIBUTION.

32:02.800 --> 32:05.451
WELL, THAT LEAVES
YOU AND ME, CLAIRE.

32:05.460 --> 32:06.654
WANT TO GO TO
THE APPLE PAN ?

32:06.660 --> 32:08.525
UH, CAN'T.

32:08.530 --> 32:10.054
I HAVE TO DO THIS...

32:10.060 --> 32:12.028
