OVERNIGHT THING...

32:12.030 --> 32:14.954
AT THE OBSERVATORY
FOR SCHOOL.

32:14.960 --> 32:16.598
I DIDN'T HEAR
ABOUT THIS.

32:16.600 --> 32:17.498
I TOLD YOU.

32:17.500 --> 32:19.149
YOU PROBABLY
WEREN'T LISTENING.

32:19.160 --> 32:21.458
THAT'S THE TYPE OF THING
I WOULD LISTEN TO.

32:22.860 --> 32:26.057
DAVID AND NATE DID IT WHEN
THEY WENT TO BONAVENTURE.

32:27.800 --> 32:29.199
DAVID,
YOU DID THIS ?

32:29.200 --> 32:31.054
UH, YEAH,
I HAD TO.

32:31.060 --> 32:32.698
YOU TOO, NATE ?

32:32.700 --> 32:33.792
YUP.

32:33.800 --> 32:35.529
BACK THEN WE THOUGHT
PLUTO WAS A PLANET.

32:35.530 --> 32:38.249
WHEN DID PLUTO
STOP BEING A PLANET ?

32:38.260 --> 32:39.693
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

32:39.700 --> 32:42.498
WELL, I SUPPOSE IT'S
OKAY FOR YOU TO GO.

32:45.960 --> 32:49.418
( Bernard )
LUCKILY GARETH ISN'T
GOING TO PRESS CHARGES,

32:49.430 --> 32:52.649
BUT I DID PROMISE HIM
THAT STEPS WOULD BE TAKEN

32:52.660 --> 32:54.355
TO REMEDY
THE SITUATION.

32:54.360 --> 32:57.727
I WISH I HAD BEEN THERE TO SEE
THE LOOK ON FEINBERG'S FACE.

32:57.730 --> 32:59.789
I'M SURE HE STARTED WITH
HIS WHOLE BLINKING THING.

32:59.800 --> 33:02.928
BRENDA, WE HAVE
A SERIOUS PROBLEM.

33:05.330 --> 33:07.651
OKAY, I'LL TALK
TO BILLY'S DOCTOR,

33:07.660 --> 33:09.992
SEE IF HE NEEDS TO BE
ON DIFFERENT MEDICATION.

33:10.000 --> 33:11.558
ACTUALLY, WE WERE
THINKING OF SOMETHING

33:11.560 --> 33:13.448
A LITTLE
MORE INVOLVED.

33:13.460 --> 33:14.927
YOUR MOTHER AND I FEEL
THAT HE NEEDS TO GO AWAY

33:14.930 --> 33:16.454
FOR INTENSIVE THERAPY.

33:16.460 --> 33:20.123
THERE'S A VERY GOOD
FACILITY IN COLORADO.

33:20.130 --> 33:22.052
YOU WANT TO PUT BILLY
IN AN INSTITUTION ?

33:22.060 --> 33:25.621
OH, PLEASE, LET'S NOT TURN
THIS INTO A 19505 B MOVIE.

33:25.630 --> 33:29.020
THIS PLACE IS RUN BY EXCELLENT
PSYCHIATRIC SPECIALISTS

33:29.030 --> 33:30.292
WHO MAY HAVE SOME...

33:30.300 --> 33:33.952
CREATIVE SOLUTION
TO HELP BILLY.

33:34.600 --> 33:37.125
YOU WANT TO GIVE BILLY
SHOCK TREATMENT.

33:37.130 --> 33:38.427
DARLING, REALLY,

33:38.430 --> 33:40.523
THIS DRAMATIC STREAK, AREN'T
YOU A LITTLE OLD FOR IT ?

33:40.530 --> 33:41.997
AND JUST FOR
THE RECORD,

33:42.000 --> 33:44.298
ELECT ROCONVULSIVE THERAPY
HAS HAD A REAL RESURGENCE

33:44.300 --> 33:47.019
IN THE LAST 10 YEARS,
WITH VERY IMPRESSIVE RESULTS.

33:47.030 --> 33:48.190
YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.497
YOUR MOTHER AND I
THINK IT'S BEST.

33:49.500 --> 33:51.388
IT CERTAINLY MAKES
YOUR LIVES EASIER.

33:51.400 --> 33:52.890
GOD FORBID BILLY
SHOULD EMBARRASS YOU

33:52.900 --> 33:55.095
IN FRONT OF YOUR STUPID
FAT CELEBRITY FRIENDS.

33:55.100 --> 33:56.829
UNFORTUNATELY,
HE IS AN ADULT.

33:56.830 --> 33:58.559
WHICH MEANS YOU CAN'T
HAVE HIM COMMITTED

33:58.560 --> 34:00.221
UNLESS HE DOES
SOMETHING DANGEROUS.

34:01.300 --> 34:02.551
DARLING...

34:03.960 --> 34:06.155
WE WERE THINKING THAT
IF YOU TALKED TO HIM,

34:06.160 --> 34:07.991
EXPLAINED HOW IT
WOULD HELP HIM.

34:08.000 --> 34:09.922
FUCK YOU BOTH.

34:09.930 --> 34:11.659
YOU'RE OUT OF
YOUR MINDS.

34:14.700 --> 34:16.918
( door closing )

34:19.130 --> 34:21.553
HI, I'M ANGELA.

34:21.560 --> 34:23.357
YOU MUST BE RUTH.

34:23.360 --> 34:24.850
YES.

34:32.160 --> 34:34.048
I SPILLED SOME BEET SALAD
ON SOMEONE'S WIG,

34:34.060 --> 34:36.449
SO, DAVID SAID
I SHOULD EAT UP HERE.

34:36.460 --> 34:37.825
I GOT THE STAINS OUT.

34:37.830 --> 34:39.991
EVERYONE IN MY FAMILY
GETS CANCER, SO...

34:40.000 --> 34:43.959
I KNOW TONS ABOUT
TAKING CARE OF WIGS.

34:45.600 --> 34:47.750
IS THAT YOURS ?

34:47.760 --> 34:49.557
THE HAIR, I MEAN.

34:49.560 --> 34:52.028
AS FAR AS I KNOW.

34:52.030 --> 34:53.622
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

34:53.630 --> 34:55.825
THANK YOU.

34:56.930 --> 34:58.989
I DON'T WANT TO BE ONE OF
THOSE MENOPAUSAL WOMEN

34:59.000 --> 35:02.492
YOU KNOW, THAT GOES ALL DIKEY
WITH THE BUTCH HAIRCUT.

35:06.830 --> 35:09.594
SO, NATE SAYS THAT
YOU'RE DATING A HAIRDRESSER.

35:09.600 --> 35:12.296
THAT IS SO LUCKY.

35:12.300 --> 35:14.120
IF HE'S ANY GOOD,
I'D LOVE TO KNOW

35:14.130 --> 35:15.927
IF HE CAN DO ANYTHING
WITH THIS MOP.

35:15.930 --> 35:18.023
DOES YOUR BOYFRIEND
COME AROUND ?

35:18.030 --> 35:21.295
