if I go by myself.

36:08.130 --> 36:10.394
You should probably just
not worry about it, okay ?

36:11.760 --> 36:13.990
Thank you for
trying to...

36:15.700 --> 36:17.349
Look, just...

36:17.360 --> 36:18.998
thank you.

36:19.700 --> 36:21.156
So, that's...

36:21.160 --> 36:23.128
that's it, I guess.

36:24.930 --> 36:26.249
Bye, Claire.

36:30.730 --> 36:32.857
THIS IS DISGUSTING.

36:32.860 --> 36:34.259
YOU HAVE CRAP IN HERE
FROM THE 805.

36:34.260 --> 36:35.796
BILLY, I'LL GET
A PLUMBER.

36:35.800 --> 36:37.449
SOMEBODY WHO ACTUALLY
KNOWS WHAT THEY'RE DOING.

36:40.560 --> 36:41.822
WOULD YOU
LOOK AT ME ?

36:41.830 --> 36:43.525
I'D REALLY LIKE TO
TALK TO YOU.

36:45.660 --> 36:48.857
I TAKE IT YOU SPOKE
TO MOM AND DAD.

36:51.460 --> 36:53.496
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
HAPPENED THAT DAY.

36:53.500 --> 36:56.719
YOU KNOW, I WAS ON NEW MEDS,
THEY WEREN'T WORKING.

36:56.730 --> 36:58.220
IT WASN'T MY FAULT.

36:59.060 --> 37:00.527
BUT DON'T WORRY.

37:00.530 --> 37:02.452
I'VE ALREADY BEEN
TO MY DOCTOR

37:02.460 --> 37:05.054
AND CHANGED
MY DOSAGE.

37:05.060 --> 37:07.199
AND I ALREADY
FEEL MORE EVEN.

37:07.200 --> 37:10.920
BILLY, I NEED TO KNOW IF
I SHOULD BE WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

37:13.800 --> 37:15.552
YOU SHOULDN'T.

37:18.130 --> 37:19.722
I SWEAR.

37:20.660 --> 37:22.594
YEAH ?
YEAH.

37:49.530 --> 37:52.454
MY GOD, YOU COULD
EAT OFF THIS SKIN.

37:54.500 --> 37:56.593
ANGELA DOES HER JOB
PERFECTLY.

37:56.600 --> 37:58.818
WHAT ABOUT THOSE HAIRS
IN HER MOLE ?

37:58.830 --> 38:01.025
RICO WOULD NEVER
HAVE LEFT THOSE THERE.

38:01.030 --> 38:03.624
ANGELA HAD A LONG
PHILOSOPHICAL
DEBATE ABOUT IT

38:03.630 --> 38:06.428
AND DECIDED THE NIECES
WOULD WANT TO REMEMBER HER

38:06.430 --> 38:08.159
EXACTLY HOW SHE WAS.

38:08.160 --> 38:10.196
I'D LIKE TO KNOW
THE MEANING OF THIS.

38:10.200 --> 38:13.499
NIKOLAI IS PICKING ME
UP TO GO TO DINNER

38:13.500 --> 38:16.492
AND I WAS PLANNING TO
SERVE HIM SHERRY BEFOREHAND.

38:16.500 --> 38:18.889
I WANTED TO
USE THE GOBLETS

38:18.900 --> 38:20.720
I GOT FROM MY COUSIN HANNAH'S
TRIP TO DRESDEN.

38:20.730 --> 38:22.391
NOW, I CAN'T BECAUSE
SOMEONE BROKE THIS

38:22.400 --> 38:24.322
AND HOPED
I WOULDN'T NOTICE IT.

38:24.330 --> 38:25.752
WHICH ONE OF YOU
DID THIS ?

38:25.760 --> 38:26.920
IT WASN'T ME.

38:26.930 --> 38:28.158
WELL, IT WASN'T ME.

38:30.830 --> 38:32.149
IT WAS ANGELA.

38:32.160 --> 38:34.856
OH, IT WAS
DEFINITELY ANGELA.

38:43.030 --> 38:44.190
HI.

38:44.200 --> 38:45.519
DAVID.

38:45.530 --> 38:46.827
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE ?

38:46.830 --> 38:49.355
I VOLUNTEER WITH THESE GUYS
A COUPLE OF TIMES A WEEK.

38:49.360 --> 38:51.794
OH, I JUST STARTED.

38:51.800 --> 38:53.097
YOU NEED SOME HELP ?

38:53.100 --> 38:55.318
YEAH, SURE.

39:09.660 --> 39:11.594
DAVID, DAVID--

39:12.530 --> 39:13.895
DAVID !

39:13.900 --> 39:15.197
I'M DYING.

39:15.200 --> 39:16.349
NO, YOU CAN'T.

39:16.360 --> 39:19.488
NOT BEFORE WE MAKE LOVE
ONE LAST TIME...

39:22.160 --> 39:23.821
OKAY.

39:23.830 --> 39:23.898
THOUGHT YOU WERE
GONNA HELP.

39:29.130 --> 39:30.688
SO, HOW'VE YOU BEEN ?

39:30.700 --> 39:32.053
GOOD, YOU ?

39:32.060 --> 39:33.721
I'M OKAY.

39:35.260 --> 39:37.023
I'VE DRIVEN BY THIS MINI-MALL
HUNDREDS OF TIMES,

39:37.030 --> 39:38.497
BUT I NEVER KNEW
THIS PLACE EXISTED.

39:38.500 --> 39:40.923
IS BEST RESTAURANT
IN ALL OF LOS ANGELES.

39:40.930 --> 39:43.057
AND NOT OUTRAGEOUS
PRICES TOO.

39:43.060 --> 39:45.824
( speaking Russian )

39:47.200 --> 39:48.827
LOTTE, IRINA.

39:48.830 --> 39:50.252
WHAT A SURPRISE
THIS IS.

39:50.260 --> 39:53.650
YOU USUALLY DO NOT COME
IN ON TUESDAY NIGHTS.

39:53.660 --> 39:55.924
CAN WE JOIN YOU ?

39:55.930 --> 39:57.124
PLEASE.

39:57.130 --> 39:59.553
MAYBE ANOTHER TIME.

39:59.560 --> 40:02.393
NO, NO, SHE SAYS
IT'S OKAY.

40:03.700 --> 40:06.453
SO, YOU MUST BE NICKY'S
SPECIAL FRIEND

40:06.460 --> 40:08.724
WE KEEP HEARING
ALL ABOUT.

40:08.730 --> 40:10.618
YOU MUST BE THINKING
OF SOMEONE ELSE.

40:10.630 --> 40:11.597
NO.

40:11.600 --> 40:13.022
YOU LOST
YOUR HUSBAND.

40:13.030 --> 40:14.691
YOU WORK
FOR NICKY.

40:14.700 --> 40:17.260
YOU USED TO
FIX DEAD PEOPLE.

40:17.260 --> 40:19.899
OH, I SUPPOSE
THAT IS ME.

40:19.900 --> 40:22.460
THIS IS RUTH.

40:24.330 --> 40:26.992
SO, THAT GUY I SAW YOU
WITH AT THE CLUB,

40:27.000 --> 40:28.297
IS THAT
A SERIOUS THING ?

40:28.300 --> 40:29.358
EDDIE ?

40:29.360 --> 40:30.725
AH...

40:30.730 --> 40:32.027
NOT REALLY.

40:32.030 --> 40:33.793
NOT YET.

40:34.430 --> 40:36.125
THOSE DRUGS
I SAW YOU TAKING,

40:36.130 --> 40:38.052
IS THAT
A SERIOUS THING ?

40:38.060 --> 40:40.927
NO, NO, I JUST
TRIED THEM ONCE.

40:40.930 --> 40:43.296
I DON'T THINK I'LL BE
TRYING THEM AGAIN.

40:43.300 --> 40:45.256
I'M GLAD TO HEAR
YOU SAY THAT.

40:45.260 --> 40:46.955
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT SHIT
HAS DONE TO MY SISTER.

40:46.960 --> 40:50.123
IT CAN SERIOUSLY
FUCK UP YOUR LIFE, DAVID.

40:51.400 --> 40:53.425
I'D HATE TO
SEE THAT HAPPEN.

40:54.830 --> 40:56.320
IT WAS STUPID,
I KNOW.

40:56.330 --> 40:57.695
I WAS JUST--

40:59.930 --> 41:02.592
YOU KNOW, RICO LEFT,
IT WAS JUST NATE AND ME.

41:02.600 --> 41:05.353
NOT THAT
IT'S AN EXCUSE.

41:07.260 --> 41:09.797
SO, WHAT'S UP WITH THAT KID
I SAW YOU WITH AT THE CLUB ?

41:09.800 --> 41:12.451
LET'S JUST SAY IT WAS
A LEARNING EXPERIENCE.

41:12.460 --> 41:13.859
EVERYONE ELSE
HAS GONE HOME.

41:13.860 --> 41:15.748
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU TWO
ARE WAITING FOR.

41:15.760 --> 41:19.252
DAVID, THIS ISN'T ONE
OF YOUR REGULAR SHIFTS.

41:19.260 --> 41:22.752
IS THERE ANY SPECIAL REASON
YOU SHOWED UP HERE TONIGHT ?

41:23.400 --> 41:25.322
NO.

41:27.200 --> 41:28.553
OH, WELL.

41:31.930 --> 41:33.795
GOODNIGHT,
YOU TWO.

41:33.800 --> 41:35.290
GOODNIGHT.

41:38.130 --> 41:39.688
YOU HUNGRY ?

41:39.700 --> 41:42.453
I'M ALWAYS HUNGRY.

41:43.960 --> 41:46.849
( Russian music)

42:16.630 --> 42:18.359
YOU FUCKING BITCH !

42:18.360 --> 42:21.158
I WOULD LIKE TO
TEAR YOUR HEART OUT

42:21.160 --> 42:23.822
LIKE YOU HAVE
TORN OUT MINE.

42:26.030 --> 42:29.124
THERE'S SUPPOSED TO BE A PICTURE
OF NATE PEEING ON A WALL.

42:29.130 --> 42:30.051
I SEE IT.

42:30.060 --> 42:31.254
I DON'T.

42:31.260 --> 42:33.626
FOUR FROM THE LEFT.

42:33.630 --> 42:36.258
OH, MY GOD.

42:36.260 --> 42:38.421
WHAT'D YOUR MOM SAY
WHEN SHE SAW THAT ?

42:38.430 --> 42:41.820
SHE WAS KIND
OF HORRIFIED, I THINK.

42:42.230 --> 42:44.050
HOW IS YOUR MOM ?

42:44.060 --> 42:45.322
SHE'S...

42:45.330 --> 42:47.195
DATING.

42:47.200 --> 42:48.724
IT'S WEIRD.

42:48.730 --> 42:50.095
WHY ?

42:50.100 --> 42:52.898
BECAUSE SHE'S MY MOTHER,
SHE'S NOT SUPPOSED TO DATE.

42:55.630 --> 42:58.497
PEOPLE SHOULD
BE WITH PEOPLE.

43:00.930 --> 43:03.728
YEAH, SOMETIMES PEOPLE ARE
JUST TOO STUPID TO KNOW IT.

43:10.430 --> 43:12.398
HOW'S YOUR TACO ?

43:14.200 --> 43:15.724
DISGUSTING.

43:20.660 --> 43:23.493
I HAD NO IDEA ABOUT
YOU AND NIKOLAI.

43:23.500 --> 43:25.127
FOR SIX YEARS...

43:25.130 --> 43:28.122
EVERY SATURDAY NIGHT,
I COOK FOR HIM DINNER.

43:28.130 --> 43:32.089
AND THEN HE TAKE ME TO
A $2.50 MOVIE ON FAIRFAX.

43:32.100 --> 43:33.556
THEN YOU COME ALONG...

43:33.560 --> 43:35.152
AND HE STOP CALLING.

43:35.160 --> 43:37.958
I HAVE TO SEE
EVERY GODDAMN FILM

43:37.960 --> 43:40.656
THIS FREDDIE PRINZE JR. DOES,

43:40.660 --> 43:43.788
AND WHAT DO I HAVE
TO SHOW FOR IT ?

43:43.800 --> 43:45.893
I'M SORRY.

43:47.960 --> 43:50.292
DO YOU WANT TO
MARRY NICKY OR NOT ?

43:50.300 --> 43:54.418
MARRIAGE IS THE LAST THING
I WOULD EVER WANT AGAIN.

43:55.400 --> 43:58.255
MAYBE I HAVE AN AMUSING
FLIRTATION WITH NIKOLAI,

43:58.260 --> 44:00.956
BUT HE SCARES ME.

44:02.530 --> 44:03.758
BEST OF ALL,
I HAVE THIS JOB,

44:03.760 --> 44:07.025
SOMETHING I NEVER WOULD
HAVE PREDICT ED FOR MYSELF.

44:07.030 --> 44:10.022
AND I LO IT

44:10.030 --> 44:12.123
BECAUSE IT'S MINE.

44:17.460 --> 44:18.927
AND I WOULD...

44:18.930 --> 44:22.525
NEVER DO ANYTHING
TO JEOPARDIZE THAT.

44:24.330 --> 44:26.355
WHICH MEANS I SHOULD
PROBABLY JUST FINISH DINNER

44:26.360 --> 44:29.124
WITH NIKOLAI
AND GO HOME.

44:36.030 --> 44:37.327
THANK YOU.

44:37.330 --> 44:39.252
I'VE HAD THE BEST TIME
COMING TO THIS FUNNY RESTAURANT

44:39.260 --> 44:41.421
AND HAVING YOU YELL AT ME
IN THE BATHROOM.

44:47.500 --> 44:50.594
DO YOU REALIZE THE WHOLE TIME
WE WERE GOING OUT,

44:50.600 --> 44:52.625
I WAS NEVER IN
YOUR BEDROOM AT NIGHT ?

44:52.630 --> 44:53.722
WELL...

44:55.630 --> 44:57.791
YOU'RE HERE NOW,
AREN'T YOU ?

45:10.600 --> 45:13.194
WHOA, THIS IS NOT
THE DAVID I KNOW.

45:13.200 --> 45:14.929
MAYBE THIS IS
THE REAL ME.

45:14.930 --> 45:16.921
I'M NOT SURE
WE SHOULD.

45:16.930 --> 45:17.999
WHY NOT ?

45:18.000 --> 45:19.991
WELL, I'M KIND OF SEEING
SOMEBODY RIGHT NOW.

45:20.000 --> 45:20.989
I DON'T CARE.

45:21.000 --> 45:22.399
I DO.

45:23.760 --> 45:25.557
COME ON, DAVID !

45:27.030 --> 45:28.520
PLEASE, WHY'D YOU
EVEN COME UP HERE,

45:28.530 --> 45:30.418
IF YOU WEREN'T INTO
SOMETHING HAPPENING ?

45:30.430 --> 45:31.397
TO TALK TO YOU.

45:31.400 --> 45:32.856
TO SEE HOW
YOU WERE DOING.

45:32.860 --> 45:34.748
TO BE FRIENDS.

45:34.760 --> 45:36.751
I DON'T WANT TO BE FRIENDS,
I WANT TO FUCK !

45:36.760 --> 45:39.194
WELL, I'M NOT
INTO THAT.

45:39.200 --> 45:40.997
CAN'T WE
JUST HAVE SEX ?

45:41.000 --> 45:43.127
IT DOESN'T HAVE
TO MEAN ANYTHING.

45:44.600 --> 45:47.728
IT'S GETTING LATE,
I SHOULD JUST GO.

45:50.600 --> 45:53.194
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF.

45:56.830 --> 45:58.855
( door slamming )

